# Input

```scss
$list:(("very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-1","very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-2"),("very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-3","very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-4"));


```


# Formatted

```scss
$list: (
	(
		"very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-1",
		"very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-2"
	),
	(
		"very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-3",
		"very-very-very-very-very-very-long-item-4"
	)
);

```
